title: and Machine Gun Kelly
description:
Machine Gun Kelly drops in and immediately becomes a GTL favorite guest! Hear his crazy stories about filming with Randall in Puerto Rico, shooting “Bird Box” with Sandra Bullock, meeting Mark Wahlberg, going all Zac Efron on his neighbor, crushing all ping pong competition, and recording with Waka Flocka Flame. Plus, Lala surprises Randall with some new wedding plans, and they answer more of your voicemail!

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
